data.description: Welcome to this picturesque 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in highly sought-after Washoe Valley with upgrades galore! As you walk through the open-concept living space with a beautiful kitchen flowing into the living room with a warm pellet stove you will be ready to host guests anytime! Some of the multiple upgrades include kitchen appliances & hardware, a backsplash, a new well pump, gorgeous roman shades, and brand new Debell windows! Perfect home for multi-generation! Must see the *Bonus* In-law quarters that could also easily be the Primary Suite. With a separate entrance from the exterior, a bathroom, a living room and two bedrooms plus an interior access from laundry room with a sink. Permitted and ready for your warm and cozy evenings by the gas fireplace. Then step outside to the spacious yard with a large chicken coop, RV Parking, a circular drive for convenience and plenty of room to build! This is perfect blend of tranquility and country living! Also, there is a portable generator in case the power goes out your appliances are safe.
